The '''Corellian Security Force Academy''', often called just '''CorSec Academy''', was the training facility for new recruits to the [[Corellian Security Force]]. [[Remote/Legends|Remotes]] played a large part in the Academy's [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] training.

